title: Google’s products and services - About Google

headings.text:
Helpful products,
              built with you in mind
New ways to learn, explore and create
Get to know the Pixel portfolio
Browse foldables, the latest phones with Gemini, and more.
Navigate smoothly, communicate easily and stay entertained on the road.
Multitask, play games and discover new apps, all on a bigger screen.

Connect to Google apps, and monitor your health and fitness — right from your
                  wrist.

paragraphs:
Search anything on your Android phone with a simple gesture — like circling,
                      highlighting, scribbling or tapping.

Be more productive with Gemini, built right into Gmail, Docs, Sheets and
                      more.

Virtually explore a place in Maps, with details like weather and busyness to
                      help you feel like you’re really there.
Clear up blurry shots to relive your favorite moments.
Remove unwanted distractions with a quick tap.
Browse topics or connect with our specialists.

links.text:
Circle to Search


Search anything on your Android phone with a simple gesture — like circling,
                      highlighting, scribbling or tapping.

Gemini for Google Workspace
                  

Be more productive with Gemini, built right into Gmail, Docs, Sheets and
                      more.

Immersive View
                  

Virtually explore a place in Maps, with details like weather and busyness to
                      help you feel like you’re really there.

Phones
                

                  Browse foldables, the latest phones with Gemini, and more.

Auto
                

                  Navigate smoothly, communicate easily and stay entertained on the road.

Tablets
                

                  Multitask, play games and discover new apps, all on a bigger screen.

Watches
                

                  Connect to Google apps, and monitor your health and fitness — right from your
                  wrist.

Photo Unblur
                    

                      Clear up blurry shots to relive your favorite moments.

Magic Eraser
                    

                      Remove unwanted distractions with a quick tap.
